Call Ravens

This spell, which must be cast outdoors, summons dozens
of ravens to torment the target.  The birds swarm around
its head, plucking at its eyes and obscuring its sight.
A creature thus blinded is unable to fight as well as
usual and may be unable to utilize certain skills, if
it possesses them.

Command: ravens <target> (defaults to attacker)
Base Cost: 40 SP
Base Recovery: medium
Base Effect: blind
Base Duration: medium
Guild Level: 14
